od redirects my golfball using the winds-of-truth and proceeds to pelt me in the ass with the past 50 balls I have sliced(most of the balls, mind you, were 'sliced' on purpose in order to test the boundaries of love and truth).  &quot;Damn that shit hurts&quot;  Then I ask for the band-aid of love and I get it.  Then immediately slice another ball on purpose and laugh my ass off.  <br>
