1) <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I think I provided a link that clearly explains why those &quot;other sources&quot; are either fraudulent or not trustworthy. It would be interesting to see you answer the paper I provided point by point. Not that it will convince you otherwise<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
